C.R.Lin &amp; J.C.Yang
</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis box="[652,741,1045,1070]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="289">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[652,741,1045,1070]" pageId="0" pageNumber="289" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
